== Features ==
- Vertical split
- Remember tree selection
- Select "only decorate local branches"
- Diff this with selected in commit list
- Prefs grouped by area, more prefs for diff etc.
- Auto-refresh while writing commit-message / indicator when committing
- Font-Size

=== Technical ===
- PBGitRevSpecifier subclass for paths
- use [PBGitRevSpecifier ref]
- start on PBGitRemote
- Value-Transformer for "Date" column
- Quicklook with SL

=== Bikeshed ===
- Size bigger for diffs before displaying "this is a large diff"
- @class-forward declaration when writing new code

=== Bugs ===
- Hunk-stage with umlauts! #197

=== Other ===
- Survey-writeup
- Cleaning of Wiki / Lighthouse
- Archive-Versions of GitX on website

=== dir.git stuff #15 ===
1. edit Info.plist
2a. /System/Library/Frameworks/CoreServices.framework/Versions/A/Frameworks/LaunchServices.framework/Versions/A/Support/lsregister -r -f /Applications/GitX.app or
2b. /System/Library/Frameworks/CoreServices.framework/Versions/A/Frameworks/LaunchServices.framework/Versions/A/Support/lsregister -u -r -f /Applications/GitX.app
(Load and unload).

Also: /usr/libexec/PlistBuddy -c "Print LSHandlers:10" ~/Library/Preferences/com.apple.LaunchServices.plist
